1. Installation

  Requirements:
    You need `yaal' library to be installed on your system
    to build and run `huginn'.

  Compilation & Installation:

    It is quite simple, really, all you have to do is run:
    
    % make

    That is all.

    You really want to stop here, do not go any further!
    
    Now, if compilation succeeded you can become root and install `huginn':
    
    % su
    # make install
    
    then you may at your opinion suid program:
    
    # chmod 4755 /usr/local/bin/`huginn'
    
  Running:


